  <entry>
    <title>使用Hexo</title>
    <link href="https://sdjk.github.io/2018/10/21/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo/"/>
    <id>https://sdjk.github.io/2018/10/21/使用Hexo/</id>
    <published>2018-10-21T13:40:42.097Z</published>
    <updated>2018-10-21T13:45:02.283Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>利用GitHub Pages和Hexo<sup id="fnref:0"><a href="#fn:0" rel="footnote">0</a></sup>搭建一个blog</p></blockquote><p>[toc]</p><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><blockquote><p>本机需要安装了git和node.js</p></blockquote><h3 id="安装git"><a href="#安装git" class="headerlink" title="安装git"></a>安装git</h3><ul><li>macOS 安装完==command line tools==自带git，就是版本不是最新的。</li></ul><h3 id="安装node-js"><a href="#安装node-js" class="headerlink" title="安装node.js"></a>安装node.js</h3><blockquote><p>在macOS环境下推荐使用==nvm==安装<sup id="fnref:1"><a href="#fn:1" rel="footnote">1</a></sup></p></blockquote><h4 id="安装nvm2"><a href="#安装nvm2" class="headerlink" title="安装nvm2"></a>安装nvm<sup id="fnref:2"><a href="#fn:2" rel="footnote">2</a></sup></h4><ul><li><p>使用cURL安装：</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.33.11/install.sh | bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>重启终端机，运行命令：</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">command</span> -v nvm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>终端没有响应，是因为没有==.bash_profile==<sup id="fnref:3"><a href="#fn:3" rel="footnote">3</a></sup>文件。</li></ul></li><li><p>创建==.bash_profile==文件</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">touch ~/.bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>再次运行安装脚本。</li></ul></li><li><p>重启终端，运行命令：</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">command</span> -v nvm</span><br><span class="line">nvm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>终端返回<code>nvm</code>，安装成功。</li></ul></li></ul><h4 id="安装node-js稳定版"><a href="#安装node-js稳定版" class="headerlink" title="安装node.js稳定版"></a>安装node.js稳定版</h4><ul><li><p>使用nvm安装：</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nvm install stable</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>查看版本：</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ node -v</span><br><span class="line">v10.12.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>附带也安装了npm：</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm -v</span><br><span class="line">6.4.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装Hexo"></a>安装Hexo</h3><ul><li><p>使用npm安装：</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>-g</code>是全局（global）</li><li><code>-cli</code>是命令行界面（command-line interface）</li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="卸载"><a href="#卸载" class="headerlink" title="卸载"></a>卸载</h3><ul><li><p>使用命令：</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm uninstall hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="建站"><a href="#建站" class="headerlink" title="建站"></a>建站</h2><ul><li><p>选择自己想要的安装目录，安装：</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><div id="footnotes"><hr><div id="footnotelist"><ol style="list-style:none; padding-left: 0;"><li id="fn:0"><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; padding-right: 10px;">0.</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;"><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/</a></span><a href="#fnref:0" rev="footnote"> ↩</a></li><li id="fn:1"><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; padding-right: 10px;">1.</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;"><a href="https://yoember.com/nodejs/the-best-way-to-install-node-js/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://yoember.com/nodejs/the-best-way-to-install-node-js/</a></span><a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote"> ↩</a></li><li id="fn:2"><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; padding-right: 10px;">2.</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;"><a href="https://github.com/creationix/nvm#manual-uninstall" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/creationix/nvm#manual-uninstall</a></span><a href="#fnref:2" rev="footnote"> ↩</a></li><li id="fn:3"><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; padding-right: 10px;">3.</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top;">环境变量配置文件:<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PATH_(variable)" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PATH_(variable)</a></span><a href="#fnref:3" rev="footnote"> ↩</a></li></ol></div></div>]]></content>
    
